renderables.text: A complete master ticket could be used to transfer ownership or impersonate your galaxy on the Urbit network without your permission.
You can lose a single shard, but if you lose two shards, or your master ticket or forget your ship name, there is no way to recover it and you will no longer be able to control your galaxy.
The master ticket and ownership seed can be used to recover transfer, spawn, delegate, and management proxies.

Combine this master ticket shard with another shard to produce a master ticket or ownership seed, which can be used to activate, transfer, escape to a new sponsor, set up transfer and management proxies, set an operator, set network keys, set DNS domains, spawn stars, and recover child seeds.
This voting seed could be used to vote on behalf of your galaxy without your permission.
If you lose your voting seed, you can recover it from your master ticket or ownership seed.
The voting seed is a BIP39 mnemonic, which can be used as the master seed for a hardware wallet.
Use the voting seed to vote on proposals.
